---
title: Baked Hot Honey Chicken Breasts  with BBQ-Spiced Sweet Potatoes and Snap Peas
description: Kick up your chicken dinner with hot honey. You control the heat by adding a little or a lot of fresh jalapeños. Baked spiced sweet potato wedges and sugary snap peas help cool down this fiery meal.
